    | AddChord BarReference
    | AddPart PartIndex
    | DuplicatePart PartIndex
    | Edit
    | MovePart PartIndex PartIndex
    | RemoveBar BarReference
    | RemoveChord BarReference ChordIndex
    | RemovePart PartIndex
    | Save
